ne bo nahranil, ne?

01:13:39.962 --> 01:13:41.881
Ne. Jaz te bom.

01:13:43.341 --> 01:13:46.094
Samo jaz vas
lahko odrešim, fantje.

01:13:47.887 --> 01:13:49.514
Willie!

01:13:51.265 --> 01:13:53.225
Vem, da si tu!

01:13:54.019 --> 01:13:55.811
